HEADWORD: Nodosarine
<hw>No`do*sa"rine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Resembling in form or structure a foraminiferous shell of the genus
<gen>Nodosaria</gen>.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
